snippet.title: 02. Amber Minogue @ Paul Taylor's Happy Hour Live
snippet.description:
Season 3 - Episode 2 : I have some non-alcoholic beer (followed by real beer) with my friend, comedian, mum, podcaster, voice-over artist, Amber Minogue.

Support the show and get exclusive content here: https://www.patreon.com/paultaylor
